#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to <b>manage your "
"entire business from your phone</b>.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງເຂົ້າໃນແອັບຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອ <b>ຈັດການທຸລະກິດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານຈາກໂທລະສັບ</"
"b>.<br/>"

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers endless customization possibilities for your Library:"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ນຳສະເໜີຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ໃນການປັບແຕ່ງທີ່ບໍ່ມີທີ່ສິ້ນສຸດສຳລັບຫ້ອງສະໝຸດຂອງທ່ານ:"

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo will help you adapt your website to fit your clients' needs perfectly. "
"Easily integrate your internal policies, customize the contact form, "
"showcase your latest arrivals, and much more!"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຈະຊ່ວຍທ່ານປັບປຸງເວັບໄຊໃຫ້ແທດເໝາະກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງລູກຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງສົມບູນແບບ. ເຊື່ອມໂຍງນະໂຍບາ"
"ຍພາຍໃນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ, ປັບແຕ່ງແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່, ສະແດງສິນຄ້າມາໃໝ່ລ້າສຸດ, ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ!"

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo's Point of Sale system is designed to handle a wide array of payment "
"methods."
msgstr ""
"ລະບົບຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale) ຂອງ Odoo ຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອຮອງຮັບວິທີການຊຳລະເງິນທີ່ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ."

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, ແລ"
"ະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once you open a return order, you have two options:"
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານເປີດຄຳສັ່ງສົ່ງຄືນ, ທ່ານມີສອງທາງເລືອກ:"

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
