"າໄດ້ໂດຍກົງ."

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Return </font><font "
"style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">App</font></strong> tracks and registers"
