"style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">App</font></strong> ຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ລົງທະບຽນ ການ"
"ສົ່ງຄືນທັງໝົດຂອງລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: library
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:library.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Point of Sale "
"(PoS)</font></strong> handles all product rentals and client service "
